	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P78_is_identified_by> "A monk born in Egypt around the year 440–450. He founded the monastery of Choziba\n                      in the Holy Land around 480. In 516 he became bishop of Caesarea, but soon resigned and returned to the monastery,\n                      where he died between 520–530." .
